of girl. I respect her.

1338
00:58:36,100 --> 00:58:38,500
Hmm, do you know what I think?

1339
00:58:38,500 --> 00:58:40,900
I think you're madly in love with her.

1340
00:58:40,900 --> 00:58:43,780
Are you?

1341
00:58:43,980 --> 00:58:45,820
