00:58:49,180 --> 00:58:52,060
because you haven't the
guts to tell me the truth.

1345
00:58:52,060 --> 00:58:54,660
You're in love with
that girl, aren't you?

1346
00:58:54,660 --> 00:58:57,500
Why not admit it?

1347
00:58:58,220 --> 00:58:59,100
