01:07:25,020 --> 01:07:25,660
A what?

1487
01:07:25,660 --> 01:07:28,620
Can you do a good, big sneeze?

1488
01:07:32,180 --> 01:07:34,300
I think so.

1489
01:07:34,300 --> 01:07:37,140
[Avice inhaling]

1490
01:07:39,620 --> 01:07:42,580
I've got it. Tom, I've got it!

1491
01:07:42,580 --> 01:07:45,700
I've got it! (Tom) you got it!

1492
01:07:45,860 --> 01:07:48,500
[Mooing]

1493
01:07:48,500 --> 01:07:51,380
[Bee buzzing]

1494
01:07:51,660 --> 01:07:53,220
She's coming.

1495
01:07:53,220 --> 01:07:55,220
Don't over-dramatize, dear.

1496
01:07:55,220 --> 01:07:56,980
Just say, "Here's a telegram,"

1497
01:07:56,980 --> 01:07:59,420
as if it's the most
natural thing in the world.

1498
01:07:59,420 --> 01:08:02,300
Yes, but I hate telegrams.

1499
01:08:02,300 --> 01:08:03,740
Um, Julia, dear,

1500
01:08:03,740 --> 01:08:06,580
sit down and, uh, don't be alarmed.

1501
01:08:06,620 --> 01:08:07,220
What's happened?

1502
01:08:07,260 --> 01:08:10,300
Well, I'm afraid there's
a telegram for you.

1503
01:08:10,900 --> 01:08:13,780
Oh.

1504
01:08:18,220 --> 01:08:19,380
[Exclaims]

1505
01:08:19,380 --> 01:08:22,220
Oh, how lovely.

1506
01:08:22,220 --> 01:08:25,100
[Seagulls cawing]

1507
01:08:33,700 --> 01:08:34,700
I only realize now

1508
01:08:34,700 --> 01:08:36,940
how terribly I've missed
you all these months.

1509
01:08:36,940 --> 01:08:39,220
And I you. God, I've missed you.

1510
01:08:39,220 --> 01:08:40,980
come on, tell me all the gossip.

1511
01:08:40,980 --> 01:08:41,540
Oh, let's see.

1512
01:08:41,540 --> 01:08:44,340
Johnny Gore-Barker has run
off with Bunty Robinson.

1513
01:08:44,340 --> 01:08:45,780
- No.
- Yeah.

1514
01:08:45,780 --> 01:08:46,860
He can't have.

1515
01:08:46,900 --> 01:08:47,940
She looks like the back of a bus.

1516
01:08:47,940 --> 01:08:51,700
Oh, I don't think Johnny Gore-Barker
knows what a bus is, front or back.

1517
01:08:51,820 --> 01:08:54,100
